title: PSX PPF/XPS Patchs and Mods *fixed index*
description:
Here is a complete collection of all the ppf/xps patch's for playstation.

For people who are not in the know, these fix's in some instances remove protections checks, others give you trainers and 50/60hz pal/ntsc switchers.

Patches are Ripped from Console Copy World 2014.

PPF-O-Matic v3.0 is included to patch your img/iso/bins.

Also included is install diagrams and mod-chip hex files for all models.


** Re-ripped and fixed index's, sorry for the mess up)
